Marie A. PROCTOR, U. S. Commissioner of Immigration, at Seattle, Wash., Appellant, v. JUNG WEE LUNG, etc., Appellee. No. 7666. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Jan. 7, 1935. J. Charles Dennis, U. S. Atty., and John Ambler, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Seattle, Wash., for appellant. Landon, Landon & Wheeler, of Seattle, Wash., for appellee.

Before WILBUR and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
